snippet.title: Amber Heard Faces Tough Questions After Settlement With Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Wednesday, August 31, 2016 - Amber Heard dons all-black attire as she arrives at LAX following her $7 million divorce settlement with Johnny Depp. Amber is asked if she feels redeemed by the media for donating the settlement to charity and if Johnny played a better Willy Wonka than the late Gene Wilder. Heard recently called out Depp for sending the settlement money directly to the the ACLU and the Children’s Hospital of Los Angeles, which would allow Depp to receive a charitable tax deduction.
